com.ibm.jaggr.core.resource

Interface IResourceVisitor.Resource

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileResource.VisitorResource
    Enclosing interface:
    IResourceVisitor

    public static interface IResourceVisitor.Resource
    Defines the interface for a resource item that is visited by the tree walker. This interface should be implemented using the folder tree meta-data available to the tree walker, particularly for the getURI(), isFolder() and lastModified() methods, avoiding additional I/O calls to retrieve this information to the extent practical.

    Implementors of this interface also implement IResource interface.
